'From Squeak2.8alpha of 16 February 2000 [latest update: #1936] on 14 March 2000 at 4:34:20 pm'!"Change Set:		DropShadowNil-arDate:			14 March 2000Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a problem with a nil shadow offset."!!DropShadowMorph methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 3/14/2000 16:32'!shadowOffset	"Return the current shadow offset"	^shadowOffset ifNil:[0@0]! !!DropShadowMorph methodsFor: 'geometry' stamp: 'ar 3/14/2000 16:33'!invalidRect: damageRect	super invalidRect: (damageRect merge: (damageRect translateBy: self shadowOffset)).! !